LANGUAGE "SIC 1.0".
SCROLL STRONG omen_scroll
MODE CHANT.
PROFILE "CIVIL"


WORK MAIN WITH SIGIL UNUSED AS TEXT:
    SAY: "Entering OMEN demo.".

    RAISE OMEN "network_failure".

    IF OMEN "network_failure" IS PRESENT THEN:
        SAY: "We foresaw the network failure.".
        FALLS_TO_RUIN: "Recovered from network failure.".
    END.

    THUS WE ANSWER WITH "OMEN demo complete.".
ENDWORK
